leve.name: Observe and Protect
leve.description: The sultana has expressed her desire to accompany a caravan on its trip to Vesper Bay so that she may observe the rebuilding effort in western Thanalan. If anything were to happen to Her Grace on the trip, our organization would be ruined, and therefore we are calling upon the realm's adventurers to assist us in clearing the Sunway of creatures who may crave a royal victual.
